# 🚨 IRON RULE — GIT IS THE SOURCE OF TRUTH FOR CODE (since 2026-06-24)

Multiple AI agents (Cursor, Manus, Claude, Base) share this repo. To stop live⇄repo drift:

## Code ships through git ONLY
- **NEVER** scp / rsync / patch / hand-edit files directly on the server `/root/tradesnow`.
- Every change: edit → `git add` → `git commit` → `git push origin main`.
- Deploy: `ssh root@143.198.141.131 "/root/deploy-tradesnow.sh"` (pull --ff-only → build → pm2 restart). The script REFUSES to run if there are uncommitted tracked changes.
- Canonical branch = **main** on `git@github.com:y0505300530-pixel/tradesnow.git`.
- START of work: `git pull origin main`.  END of work: commit + push. Always.

## Why
On 2026-06-24 the deployed V4.5 was never committed → every agent saw a different codebase (phantom positions, contradictory edits). Old history also leaked secrets; `main` is now a clean orphan baseline.

## Companion truth
IBKR = source of truth for NUMBERS (prices/P&L/positions). git/GitHub = source of truth for CODE. Never trust the server working tree over git, nor TradeSnow computed numbers over IBKR. See DEPLOY_WORKFLOW.md.
